:::

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display .cell-output-markdown}
$\displaystyle A{\left(x \right)} \frac{d^{2}}{d x^{2}} y{\left(x \right)} + B{\left(x \right)} \frac{d}{d x} y{\left(x \right)} + C{\left(x \right)} y{\left(x \right)} = F{\left(x \right)}$
